text: is a Japanese boy group started through the reality competition show Produce 101 Japan. The group is managed by Lapone Entertainment, a joint company between Yoshimoto Kogyo and CJ ENM. They make J-pop and K-pop songs. It has eleven members: Issei Mamehara, Ren Kawashiri, Takumi Kawanishi, Shosei Ohira, Shion Tsurubo, Ruki Shiroiwa, Keigo Sato, Syoya Kimata, Junki Kono, Sukai Kinjo and Sho Yonashiro. ==References== Category:2020 establishments in Japan Category:2020s music groups Category:J-pop music groups Category:Japanese boy bands Category:Japanese pop music groups Category:K-pop music groups Category:Musical groups established in 2020 Category:Produce 101
